Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Fix gcc zlib fdopen macro on modern macOS

---
 ...dopen-macro-conflict-on-modern-macOS.patch | 31 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 31 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 packages/gcc/15.2.0/0011-Fix-zlib-fdopen-macro-conflict-on-modern-macOS.patch

diff --git a/packages/gcc/15.2.0/0011-Fix-zlib-fdopen-macro-conflict-on-modern-macOS.patch b/packages/gcc/15.2.0/0011-Fix-zlib-fdopen-macro-conflict-on-modern-macOS.patch
